<script>
$(function() {
    // Clicking on the component
    $('.js-monitor-click').off('click').on('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        alert('You clicked the component!');
    });

    $('.js-skip-click').off('click').on('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        alert('You clicked just this link!');
    });

    // Chart
    (function() {
        var colors = ["#006390", "#2ba644", "#000000"]; // chart colors

        var chartContainer = $('#ma-monitoring-chart').parent(),
            chartDimension = chartContainer.actual('width'),
            chartElement = chartContainer.find('.ma-monitoring-chart').attr('id');

        Highcharts.setOptions({
            colors: colors,
            exporting: {
                enabled: false
            },
            credits: {
                enabled: false
            }
        });

        $(window).off('resize.chart');
        $(window).on('resize.chart', function() {
            var d = chartContainer.actual('width');
            chart.setSize(d, d, doAnimation = false);
        });

        var chart = new Highcharts.Chart({
                series: [{
                    data: [
                        ['Bonds', 60.00],
                        ['Stocks', 30.00],
                        ['Other', 10.00]
                    ]
                }],
                chart: {
                    renderTo: chartElement,
                    type: 'pie',
                    margin: [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    spacing: [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    backgroundColor: 'transparent',
                    width: chartDimension,
                    height: chartDimension
                },
                title: false,
                tooltip: false,
                plotOptions: {
                    pie: {
                        slicedOffset: false,
                        shadow: false,
                        allowPointSelect: false,
                        startAngle: 360,
                        innerSize: '75%',
                        size: '100%',
                        dataLabels: false,
                        stickyTracking: false,
                        states: {
                            hover: false
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
    }());
});
</script>

<script>
mq.addListener(function(changed) {
    if(changed.matches) {
        // the width of browser is more then 700px
		var oldurl = '#collapseOne';
		var newurl = '#collapseOneDisable';
		$('div [href="' + oldurl + '"]').attr('href', newurl);
    } else {
        // the width of browser is less then 700px
		var oldurl = '#collapseOneDisable';
		var newurl = '#collapseOne';
		$('div [href="' + oldurl + '"]').attr('href', newurl);
    }
});

</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$.validator.setDefaults({
    submitHandler: function() {
        // alert for testing.
        alert("submitted!");
    }
});

$(document).ready(function() {

    // VALID SSN
    $.validator.addMethod('SocialSecurity',
        function(value) {
            return validSSN(value) || value == "";
        }, 'Please enter a valid SSN'
    );

    function validSSN(value) {
        var regex = /^([0-6]\d{2}|7[0-6]\d|77[0-2])([ \-]?)(\d{2})\2(\d{4})$/;
        if (!regex.test(value)) {
            return false;
        }
        var temp = value;
        if (value.indexOf("-") != -1) {
            temp = (value.split("-")).join("");
        }
        if (value.indexOf(" ") != -1) {
            temp = (value.split(" ")).join("");
        }
        if (temp.substring(0, 3) == "000") {
            return false;
        }
        if (temp.substring(3, 5) == "00") {
            return false;
        }
        if (temp.substring(5, 9) == "0000") {
            return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
    // END VALID SSN


    // CUSTOM METHOD FOR CHECKING AGE
    $.validator.addMethod("age13", function(value, element) {
        try {
            if (value != null && value.length == 10) {
                var parts = value.split("/");
                var dob = new Date(parts[2], parts[0] - 1, parts[1]);
                dob.setFullYear(dob.getFullYear() + 13);
                if (new Date() > dob) {
                    return true;
                }
            }
        } catch (err) {}
        return false;
    }, "Please re-enter date of birth, you must be at least 13 years old");
    // END AGE

    // CUSTOM METHOD TEST DATE FORMAT
    $.validator.addMethod("dateMMDDYYYY", function(value, element) {
        try {
            if (value != null && value.length == 10) {
                var parts = value.split("/");
                var dob = new Date(parts[2], parts[0] - 1, parts[1]);
                if (dob.getDate() == parts[1] && dob.getMonth() == (parts[0] - 1)) {
                    return true;
                }
            }
        } catch (err) {}
        return false;
    }, "Please enter a date in the requested format");
    // END DATE FORMAT

    // SET MASKS
    $('#dob').mask("99/99/9999", {
        placeholder: 'MM/DD/YYYY'
    });
    $('#ssn').mask("999-99-9999", {
        placeholder: '999-99-9999'
    });
	// END MASKS

    // FORM VALIDATION
    $("#demo").validate({
        rules: {
            firstname: "required",
            lastname: "required",
            username: {
                required: true,
                minlength: 2
            },
            password: {
                required: true,
                minlength: 5
            },
            confirm_password: {
                required: true,
                minlength: 5,
                equalTo: "#password"
            },
            email: {
                required: true,
                email: true
            },
            dateOfBirth: {
                required: true,
                date: true,
                dateMMDDYYYY: true,
                age13: true
            },
            ssn: {
                SocialSecurity: true
            },
			device: "required",
            agree: "required"
        },
        messages: {
            firstname: "Please enter your firstname",
            lastname: "Please enter your lastname",
            username: {
                required: "Please enter a username",
                minlength: "Your username must consist of at least 2 characters"
            },
            password: {
                required: "Please provide a password",
                minlength: "Your password must be at least 5 characters long"
            },
            confirm_password: {
                required: "Please provide a password",
                minlength: "Your password must be at least 5 characters long",
                equalTo: "Please enter the same password as above"
            },
            email: "Please enter a valid email address",

            dateOfBirth: {
                required: "Please enter a Date of Birth",
                date: "Please enter a date of birth in the requested format",
                dateMMDDYYYY: "Please enter a date of birth in the requested format"
            },
            ssn: 'Please enter a social security number.',
            agree: "Please accept our policy"
        },

        errorElement: "span",
        errorPlacement: function(error, element) {

            element.parents(".form-group").addClass("has-feedback");

            if (element.prop("type") === "checkbox") {
                error.insertAfter(element.next('label'));
            } else if (element.prop("type") === "radio") {
                error.hide();
            } else {
                error.insertAfter(element);
            }

            // Add the span element, if doesn't exists, and apply the icon classes to it.
            if (!$(element).parents('.form-group').find('span.glyphicon').length) {
                $("<span role='presentation' class='glyphicon glyphicon-remove form-control-feedback'></span>").insertBefore(element);
            }
        },
        success: function(label, element) {
            // Add the span element, if doesn't exists, and apply the icon classes to it.
            if (!$(element).parents('.form-group').find('span.glyphicon').length) {
                $("<span role='presentation' class='glyphicon glyphicon-ok form-control-feedback'></span>").insertBefore($(element));
            }
        },
        highlight: function(element, errorClass, validClass) {
            $(element).parents(".form-group").addClass("error").removeClass("success");
            $(element).parents(".form-group").find('span.glyphicon').addClass("glyphicon-remove").removeClass("glyphicon-ok");
        },
        unhighlight: function(element, errorClass, validClass) {
            $(element).parents(".form-group").addClass("success").removeClass("error");
            $(element).parents(".form-group").find('span.glyphicon').addClass("glyphicon-ok").removeClass("glyphicon-remove");
        },
    });
	// END VALIDATION


// REPLACE/HIDE CHARACTERS
function hideDOB(objId) {
    var obj = $(objId)[0];
    var v = obj.value;
    var l = v.length;
    var val = v.substr(6);
    obj.value = '**/**/' + val;
    return true;
}

hideDOB('#dob2');
});



</script>
